Ackmena is the nightshift bartender in Chalmun's Cantina in Mos Eisley on Tatooine. She is a favorite personage of the regular patrons there. Unlike Wuher, the dayshift bartender, Ackmena's friendliness and open personality livens the atmosphere of the room immensely. She has routinely lend money to needy patrons and offers free drinks on special occasions.

Tork is a bouncer of an unknown species who works at Chalmun's Cantina in Mos Eisley on Tatooine. As a bouncer, his job is to eject intoxicated customers who are causing trouble, or simply unwilling to leave after the bar is closed down. He is helped in this by his fierce appearance and his intimidating size (well over two meters tall.)
